org.apache.samoa.topology

Class AbstractProcessingItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.samoa.topology.AbstractProcessingItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IProcessingItem, ProcessingItem
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SamzaProcessingItem, ThreadsProcessingItem

    public abstract class AbstractProcessingItem
extends Object
implements ProcessingItem
    Abstract ProcessingItem Helper for implementation of ProcessingItem. It has basic information for a ProcessingItem: name, parallelismLevel and a processor. Subclass of this class needs to implement addInputStream(Stream, PartitioningScheme).
    Author:
    Anh Thu Vu
